191
00:15:19,200 --> 00:15:21,400
Rock 'n' roll, man.

192
00:15:21,400 --> 00:15:25,320
<i>Come in here, dear boy Have a cigar

193
00:15:25,320 --> 00:15:28,360
<i>You're gonna go far.</i>

