Syd had sort of gone off the idea of doing Top Of The Pops,

228
00:17:12,720 --> 00:17:14,480
and being sort of commercial.

229
00:17:14,480 --> 00:17:16,760
<i>..shoes and brought me here.</i>

230
00:17:16,760 --> 00:17:19,840
